overview.en: The Sanyan community, combined with the technology and ideas of the blockchain and the pass, has created a new “pass-through reading” model and opened the “big voyage era” of the Chinese Internet-passenging commercial revolution.
overview.zh: 三言社区，结合区块链和通证的技术和思想，打造出全新的“通证阅读”模式，开启了中国互联网通证商业革命的“大航海时代”。
